data.description: Impeccable brick home! Ready for immediate occupancy, this home boasts one of the neighborhood's largest backyards and is conveniently situated across from the common area. Enjoy the expansive screened back porch with a TV and a privacy-fenced yard. The property is equipped with Gutters and beautiful landscape lighting from Unique Lighting. The 2-car garage includes built-in shelving for storage. Living Room, Dining and Kitchen all feature hardwood flooring. Fully equipped kitchen with stainless appliances and granite countertops.  The primary bedroom showcases hardwood flooring, a vaulted ceiling, an ensuite bathroom with granite countertops, a tile shower, a jetted tub, and speakers. Brand new Water Heater. UTILITIES:  GA Power, Public Water & Sewer (with a Sump Pump), Lawn Irrigation - maintenance by Savina Plumbing, Propane tank (for fireplace) Leased with Kash Gas, High speed internet available.  Easy to show!
